space"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1,22 V (V<sub>BG</sub>)</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0 V (GND)</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">N/A</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h4>ADCSRA - ADC status register</h4>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADEN</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADSC</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADATA</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADIF</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADIE</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS2</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS1</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS0</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADEN</strong> - &nbsp;(ADC Enable)&nbsp;povoľuje prácu ADC prevodníka pri nastavení&nbsp;na logickú&nbsp;1. V opačnom prípade je AD prevodník vypnutý</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADSC</strong> - (ADC Start Conversion) aktivuje prevod AD prevodníka. Prvá konverzia inicializuje obvody potrebné k prevodu, čím doba prevodu trvá 25 cyklov oproti normálnym&nbsp;13 cyklom</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADATE</strong> - (ADC Auto Trigger Enable) pri nastavení na 1&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">aktivuje auto/samo spúšťaci mód. Prevodník je aktivovaný&nbsp;nábežnou hranou vybratého zdroja samospúšťania (bity ADTS2:0 v registri SFIOR)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADIF</strong> - (ADC Interrupt Flag) príznak prerušenia, ktorý je nastavovaný po ukončení revodu a naplnení dátového registra. Nastavuje sa aj pri zakázanom povolení globálných&nbsp;prerušení a prerušení prevodníka ADIE. Nulovaný je automaticky po vykonaní obslužnej rutiny prerušenia, alebo priamym nastavením&nbsp;&nbsp;na 1.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADPS2:0</strong> - (ADC Prescaler Select Bits) nastavuje predeličku taktovacích hodín mikroprocesora.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1" style="margin-left:25px">\r\n	<caption><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Nastavenie preddeličky taktovacích hodín</span></span></caption>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS2</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS1</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">ADPS0</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">Preddelička</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">2</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">2</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">4</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">8</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">16</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">32</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">64</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">128</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h4>SFIOR - Špeciálny register funkcií vstupu-výstupu</h4>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">ADTS2</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">ADTS1</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">ADTS0</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">ACME</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">PUD</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">PSR2</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">PSR10</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>ADTS2:0</strong> - v prípade ak je nastavený bit ADATE v ADCSRA registri, hodnota týchto bitov udáva o aký externý spúšťač prevodu AD prevodníka sa jedná. Naokpak ak je&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">bit ADATE v ADCSRA registri nulový nastavenie bitov ADTS2:0 nemá nijaký vplyv. Prevod sa spúšťa nábežnou hranou vybratým príznakom prerušenia (napr. príznakom počítadla po dopočítani na určitú hodnotu). Treba pripomenúť, že prevod začína po nábežnej hrane ak je bit ADEN v ADCSRA registri nastavený.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2016-07-12 06:33:41', NULL, 'released');
INSERT INTO `Articles` (`Id`, `Id_Users`, `Category`, `Category_unaccent`, `Title`, `Title_unaccent`, `Content`, `Registered`, `Edited`, `Type`) VALUES
(25, 1, 'Atmega8', 'atmega8', 'Diel 5 - teória SPI komunikácie', 'diel-7-teoria-spi-komunikacie', '<h3>SPI komunikácia Atmega8</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">obojsmerná komunikácia, trojvodičovým synchónnym dátovym prenosom,</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">prevádzka Master, Slave,</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">možnoť výberu LSB alebo MSB bitu ako prvého,</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">príznak prerušenia po ukončení prenosu,</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">príznak kolízie pri zápise,</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">dvojnásobná rýchlosť Master SPI módu.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Základ SPI komunikácie&nbsp;medzi Masterom a Slaveom tvoria posuvné registre a generátor taktovacích hodín Mastra. Master iniciuje začiatok komunikácie nastavením&nbsp;nízkej úrovne na pine SS&nbsp;(log. 1) požadovaného Slave-a. Následne zápisom dát do SPDR registra pri nastavení bitov SPE v SPCR registri začne prebiehať výmena.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>SPCR - kontrólny register&nbsp;SPI</h4>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPIE</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPE</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">DODR</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">MSTR</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">CPOL</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">CPHA</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPR1</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPR0</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>SPIE</strong> (SPI Interrupt Enable) - povoľuje prerušenie, ak je nastevený bit SPIF v SPSR registri a globálne prerušenia sú povolené (sei()).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>SPE</strong> (SPI Enable) -&nbsp;povoľuje chod SPI komunikácie.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>DODR&nbsp;</strong>(Data Order) - udáva, ktorý bit je posielaný ako prvý, pri nastavení na log. 1&nbsp;je posielaný ako prvý&nbsp;LSB bit, v opačnom prípade (DODR = 0) ako prvý je posielaný MSB bit.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>MSTR</strong>&nbsp;(Master/Slave Select) - výber módu Master ak MSTR = 1 a&nbsp;Slave ak&nbsp;MSTR = 0. Ak je pin SS konfigurovaný ako vstup v Master móde a je na ňom logická nula, dochádza k nulovaniu MSTR bitu a prechodu do Slave módu, pričom sa nastaví SPIF bit v SPSR registri.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPOL</strong>&nbsp;(Clock Polarity) - udáva polaritu stavu nečinnosti a aktívneho stavu. V prípade, že bit CPOL je nastavený na log.&nbsp;0, stav nečinnosti je log. 0 a aktívny stav je log. 1. V opačnom prípade, ak CPOL je nastavený na log. 1, stav nečinnosti je log. 1 a aktívny stav je log. 0.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPHA</strong>&nbsp;(Phase Polarity) - udáva fázovy posun medzi dátami a hodinovým impulzom CLK.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>SPR1:0</strong>&nbsp;(SPI Clock Rate Select 1 a 0) - prostredníctvom týchto bitov a bitu SPI2X v registri SPSR sa nastavuje rýchlosť taktovacích impulzov na píne SCK v Master móde, preddelička taktovacích hodín.</span></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1">\r\n		<caption><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Nastavenie preddeličky taktovacích hodín</span></span></caption>\r\n		<thead>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<th scope="col"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">SPI2X</span></span></th>\r\n				<th scope="col"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">SPR1</span></span></th>\r\n				<th scope="col"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">SPR0</span></span></th>\r\n				<th scope="col"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">SCK Frekvencia</span></span></th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/4</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/16</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/64</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/128</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/2</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/8</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/32</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n				<td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">f<sub>OSC</sub>/64</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Módy komunikácie CPOL a CPHA</span></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Pri SPI komunikácií existujú 4 spôsoby (módy) prenosu dát, ktoré hlavným cieľom je zlepšiť&nbsp;flexibilitu komunikácie medzi rôznymi zariadeniami. Jedná sa o časový okamih, kedy dochádza&nbsp;k čítaniu a zmene jednotlivých bitov.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPOL = 0, CPHA = 0</strong> - stav nečinnosti je definovaný log. 0, aktívny stav log. 1. Pri nábežnej hrane CP</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">OL a stabilnej úrovne hodinového impulzu CLK</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;(stabilná&nbsp;úrovren)&nbsp;dochádza k čítaniu dát</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"> a počas zostupnej hrany </span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">taktovacích hodín CPOL, kedy zároveň dochádza k preklápaniu hodinového impulzu CLK,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">k&nbsp;posuvu bitu (zmene dát).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPOL = 1, CPHA = 0</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;stav nečinnosti je definovaný log. 1, aktívny stav log. 0. Pri zostupnej hrane CP</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">OL a stabilnej úrovne hodinového impulzu CLK</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;(stabilná&nbsp;úrovren)&nbsp;dochádza k čítaniu dát</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">&nbsp;a počas nábežnej hrany&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">taktovacích hodín CPOL, kedy zároveň dochádza k preklápaniu hodinového impulzu CLK,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">k&nbsp;posuvu bitu (zmene dát).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPOL = 0, CPHA = 1</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;stav nečinnosti je definovaný log. 0, aktívny stav log. 1. Čitanie dát prebieha počas preklápania&nbsp;hodinového taktu (</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">dáta nie sú stabilné</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">) a nábežnej hrany CPOL. Počas stabilnej úrovne dochádza k zmene údajov (posuvu bitu) a zostupnej hrany CPOL.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CPOL = 1, CPHA = 1</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">stav nečinnosti je definovaný log. 1, aktívny stav log. 0.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Čitanie dát prebieha&nbsp;počas preklápania&nbsp;hodinového taktu (</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">dáta nie sú&nbsp;stabilné</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">) a zostupnej hrany CPOL. Počas stabilnej úrovne dochádza k zmene údajov (posuvu bitu) a nábežnej hrany CPOL.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega8/SPI.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega8/SPI.png" style="height:220px; width:350px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Obr. 1 - Časový diagram módov SPI komunikácie [<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_timing_diagram" style="color: blue" target="_blank">wiki</a>]</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>SPSR - status register&nbsp;SPI</h4>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1" style="line-height:20.8px">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPIF</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">WCOL</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">SPI2X</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>SPIF (SPI Interrupt Flag)</strong> - príznak prerušenia SPI, ktorý je nastavovaný po ukončení výmeny dát. Prerušenie je generované v prípade povolných globálnych prerušení a príznaku SPIE v SPCR registri. V prípade ak je zariadenie zvolené za Master, pin SS je nastavený ako vstupný a objaví sa na ňom úroveň log. 0, dochádza tiež k nastaveniu tohto príznaku. Príznak sa nuluje hardwarovo počas vykoavania obslužnej rutiny prerušenia. Súčasne je nulovaný prvým prečítaním po nastavení na log. 1&nbsp;v&nbsp;SPSR registri a prístupom SPI Data Register (SPDR).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>WCOL (Write Collision Flag)</strong> - je nastavený ak je pokus o zápis dát do SPDR registra počas výmený dát. Nulovaný je prvým prečítaním po jeho nastavení vo SPSR registri a následným prístupom dát v SPDR registri.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong>SPI2X (Double SPI Speed Bit)</strong> - umožňuje nastaviť preddeličku na dvojnásobnú rýchlosť. Najnižšia hodnota je f<sub>clk</sub>/2.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align:justify">SPDR - dátový register&nbsp;SPI</h4>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="1" style="line-height:20.8px">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">MSB</span></span></th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope="col" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">LSB</span></span></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">R/W</span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">R/W</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Dátový register, ktorý slúži na prenos údajov medzi Register File a SPI posuvným registrom. Zápisom do registra je inicializovaný prenos. Čitanie&nbsp;registra spôsobí prečítanie buffra posuvného registra.</span></span></p>\r\n', '2016-08-17 11:28:56', NULL, 'released'),
(26, 1, 'Atmega16', 'atmega16', 'Diel 2 - návrh osciloskopu', 'diel-2-navrh-osciloskopu', '<h3>Osciloskop v podaní Atmega16</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Základom tvorby jednoduchého osciloskopu je Atmega16, u ktorej bude využitý&nbsp;čítač a AD&nbsp;prevodník. Teória k AD prevodníku je popísana v kapitole&nbsp;<a href="http://poznamkovyblog.cekuj.net/admin/atmega16/detail/diel-1-teoria-ad-prevodnika/24/" style="color:#0033ff;" target="_blank">Diel 1 - teória AD prevodníka</a>. Samotný obvod je zložený z nasledujúcich komponentov:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">1x ATmega16A-PU (40 pinové prevedenie) -&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gme.sk/atmega16-16pu-pdip40-atmel" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/atmega16-16pu-pdip40-atmel</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">1x&nbsp;oscilátor 16 MHz -&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gme.sk/krystal-hc49-u-q-16mhz" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/krystal-hc49-u-q-16mhz</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">2x 22pF keramické kondenzátory -&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gme.sk/cks1206-22p-50v-npo-5-yageo" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/cks1206-22p-50v-npo-5-yageo</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">1x 10µH tlmivka -&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gme.sk/tlumivka-axialni-tl-10uh-ec24" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/tlumivka-axialni-tl-10uh-ec24</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">3x 0,1µF/T tantálové kondenzátory -&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gme.sk/cts-100n-35v-a-20-yhc-ca45" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/cts-100n-35v-a-20-yhc-ca45</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">4x 10k<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">Ω rezistor -&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.gme.sk/ru-10k-0207-0-25w-5" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/ru-10k-0207-0-25w-5</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">3x tlačidlo -&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.gme.sk/mikrospinac-do-dps-tc-0107-t" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/mikrospinac-do-dps-tc-0107-t</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">1x 6pinový ISP konektor (samec) -&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.gme.sk/konektor-mlw06a-con" target="_blank">https://www.gme.sk/konektor-mlw06a-con</a></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">1x lcd displej 1.8 TFT LCD</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_scheme_st7735.png" target="_blank"><img alt="Schéma jednoduchého osciloskopu" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_scheme_st7735.png" style="height:353px; width:500px" /></a></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><strong><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Obr. 1 - Schéma zapojenia osciloskopu s 1.8 TFT LCD</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11px"><strong><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/pcb_st7735_equipments.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/pcb_st7735_equipments.png" style="height:454px; width:500px" /></a></span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><strong>Obr. 2&nbsp;- Návrh plošného&nbsp;spoja zapojenia osciloskopu - osadenie súčiastok</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11px"><strong><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/pcb_st7735_polygon.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/pcb_st7735_polygon.png" style="height:454px; width:500px" /></a><br />\r\nObr. 3 - Návrh plošného&nbsp;spoja zapojenia osciloskopu - st7735</span></strong></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_bottom_st7735.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_bottom_st7735.jpg" style="height:281px; width:500px" /></a><br />\r\nObr. 4&nbsp;- Plošný&nbsp;spoj&nbsp;zapojenia osciloskopu - st7735</strong></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_top_st7735.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/oscilloscop/atmega16_top_st7735.jpg" style="height:281px; width:500px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11px">Obr. 4&nbsp;- Osadenie osciloskopu - st7735</span></span></strong></p>\r\n', '2016-08-21 19:28:58', NULL, 'released');
INSERT INTO `Articles` (`Id`, `Id_Users`, `Category`, `Category_unaccent`, `Title`, `Title_unaccent`, `Content`, `Registered`, `Edited`, `Type`) VALUES
(27, 1, 'Atmega8', 'atmega8', 'Diel 6 - teória kontroléra pcd852', 'diel-6-teoria-s-kontrolerom-pcd852', '<h3 style="text-align:justify">Teória radiča&nbsp;displeja&nbsp;Nokia 5110</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">PCD852 je nízkoenergetický CMOS LCD kontrolér/driver navrhnútý na riadenie grafického displeja so 48 riadkami a 84 stĺpcami. S mikrokontrolérom pracuje prostredníctvom sériového rozhania. Charakteristické parametre PCD852:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">48 riadkov, 84 stĺpcov&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">pamäť displeja 48 x 84 bitov (</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">RAM)</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">sériová komunikácia do 4 Mbits/s</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">externý resetovací vstupný pin</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">multiplexný pomer 48</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">napájacie napätie v rozmedzí 2,7 až 3,3 V</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">napájacie napätie displeja 6,0 až 8,5 V pre interné napájanie a 6 až 9 V pre externé napájanie</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">nizkonenergetické prevedenie vhodné pre napájanie batériou</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">tepelná kompenzácia</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">rozsah teplôt okolia -25 až +70 °C</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega8/pcd852/nokia-lcd-back.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="Predná strana lcd displeja Nokia 5110 s radičom pcd852" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega8/pcd852/nokia-lcd-front.jpg" style="height:400px; width:400px" /><img alt="Zadná strana lcd displeja Nokia 5110 s radičom pcd852" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega8/pcd852/nokia-lcd-back.jpg" style="height:400px; width:400px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><strong><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Obr. 1 - LCD displej z Nokie 5110 s radičom pcd852</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">V článku bude&nbsp;načrtnútý&nbsp;príklad&nbsp;prepojenia a komunikácie lcd displeja s&nbsp;miktrokontrolérom rady Atmega8 / Atmega16 u ktorých je využitá SPI&nbsp;komunikácia&nbsp;(MOSI, SCK, SS). Signál MISO nie je využitý, keďže sa jedna iba o jednosmerný prenos dát - z mikrokontroléra do ovládača displeja.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Označenie a význam portov</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>RST</strong> (RESET) - externý&nbsp;resetovací impulz&nbsp;(aktívna úroveň log. 0). Trvanie impulzu by nemalo byť menej ako 100 ns.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CE</strong> (CHIP ENABLED) - povoľuje činnosť s radičom / kontrolérom (aktívna úroveň log. 0).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>DC</strong> (DATA COMMAND) - definuje typ príjmaných dát (dáta - log. 1 /&nbsp;príkaz - log. 0).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>DIN </strong>(DATA INPUT)<strong>&nbsp;</strong>- vstupný port pre dáta / príkaz.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>CLK</strong>&nbsp;(CLOCK) - hodinový impulz.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>UCC</strong>&nbsp;- napájacie napätie 2,7 až 3,3 V.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>LIGHT</strong>&nbsp;- nastavenie kontrastu (v obvyklom prípade&nbsp;uzemnené).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><strong>GND</strong>&nbsp;- uzemnenie.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Tvorba knižnice</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Prvým krokom je vytvorenie a privedenie resetovacieho impulzu na pin RST, pretože po pripojení napájania lcd displeja sú obsahy všetkých registrov a pamäte RAM nedefinované.&nbsp;Resetovací impulz musí byť aplikovaný najneskôr do 100 ms po pripojení napätia. Dĺžka impulzu by nemala byť kratšia ako 100 ns. Charakter alebo tvar impulzu je&nbsp;"U", t. j. z log. 1 do log. 0 a&nbsp;do log. 1.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:#800080"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">#define PORT PORTB<br />\r\n#define RST &nbsp;PB4</span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">// Rseset Impulse&nbsp;shape with times</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#0000CD"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">// ____</span></span><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">________&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; _________</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px">// &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; __________</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px">// |&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:9px">max 100 ms</span><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp; | <span style="font-size:9px">min 0.1 ms</span>&nbsp;|</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><strong><span style="color:#006400">void</span></strong> <strong>ResetImpulse</strong> (<strong><span style="color:#006400">void</span></strong>)<br />\r\n{<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// Actiavte pull-up register&nbsp;logical high on pin RST</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; PORT |= (1 &lt;&lt; RST);<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// Reset as output</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; DDR &nbsp;|= (1 &lt;&lt; RST);<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// delay 1ms</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; _delay_ms(1);<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// Reset Low</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; PORT &amp;= ~(1 &lt;&lt; RST);<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// delay 1ms</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; _delay_ms(1);<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// Reset High</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; PORT |= &nbsp;(1 &lt;&lt; RST);<br />\r\n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Po resetovacom impulze je&nbsp;ovládač inicializovaný&nbsp;do východzích nastavení:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Power down mode PD = 1 (čip je neakívny)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Horizontálne adresovanie (bit V = 0), normálna adresná sada (bit H = 0)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Displej prázdny (bit E = D = 0)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Adresný čítač ja nastavený na 0 (X<sub>6</sub> do&nbsp;X<sub>0</sub> = 0; Y<sub>2</sub></span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;do</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;Y<sub>0</sub> = 0</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Tepelný koeficient&nbsp;ovládača TC<sub>1</sub>, TC<sub>0</sub> = 0</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px">BIAS (prahová hodnota) BS2, BS0 = 0</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px">Napätie U<sub>lcd</sub> je rovné 0, HV generátor je vypnutý (VOP<sub>6</sub> až&nbsp;VOP<sub>0</sub> = 0)</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px">Po zapnutí je obsah pamäte RAM nedefinovaný</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Druhým krokom je nastavenie a povolenie sériovej komunikácie (SPI). Komunikácia SPI&nbsp;závisí od typu mikrokontroléra. Potup nastavenia&nbsp;a spustenia SPI u&nbsp;mikrokontrolérov Atmega8 a&nbsp;Atmega16 je v podstate rovnaký, základom&nbsp;je správne nastaviť&nbsp;kontrolný&nbsp;register&nbsp;SPCR.&nbsp;(POZOR!!!&nbsp;piny SPI sú u rôznych mikrokontroléroch vyvedené&nbsp;rôzne, napr.&nbsp;Atmega8 má signál MOSI&nbsp;na&nbsp;pine PB3 ale&nbsp;Atmega16 na&nbsp;pine PB5). SPI komunikácia mikrokontroléra Atmega8&nbsp;je popísaná v článku<strong> <a href="http://poznamkovyblog.cekuj.net/admin/atmega8/detail/diel-5-teoria-spi-komunikacie/25/" target="_blank">Diel 5 - teória SPI komunikácie</a></strong>. V registri SPCR sú&nbsp;nastavené&nbsp;bity SPE (povolenie komunikácie), MSTR (mikrokontrolér v&nbsp;Master móde) a preddelička, t.j.&nbsp;rýchlosť prenosu, pomocou bitov&nbsp;SPR0 a SPR1. V tomto prípade je&nbsp;preddelička definovaná f<sub>clk</sub>/16, čo predstavuje frekvenciu 1MHz. t.j. nastavuje sa&nbsp;iba bit&nbsp;SPR0.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205)"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">// @descr Inicializácia SPI komunikácie<br />\r\n// @param void&nbsp;</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:rgb(0, 100, 0)"><strong>void</strong></span>&nbsp;<strong>SpiInit&nbsp;</strong>(<strong>void</strong>)<br />\r\n{<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#0000CD">// SPE &nbsp;- povolenie SPI komunikácie<br />\r\n&nbsp; // MSTR - zariadenie ako Master<br />\r\n&nbsp; // SPR0 - preddelička&nbsp;fclk/16 = 1MHz</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; SPCR |= (1 &lt;&lt; SPE)&nbsp;|&nbsp;(1 &lt;&lt; MSTR) |&nbsp;(1 &lt;&lt; SPR0);<br />\r\n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Prenos dát prostredníctvom SPI je inicializovaný&nbsp;uložením dát do dátového registra SPDR. Na posielanie príkazov je vytvorená funkcia&nbsp;<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>CommandSend()</strong></span>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:#0000CD"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">// @descr Posielanie príkazov<br />\r\n// @param uint8_t&nbsp;</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#006400"><strong>void</strong></span> <strong>CommandSend&nbsp;</strong>(<strong><span style="color:#006400">uint8_t</span></strong> data)<br />\r\n{</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">// povolenie komunikácie&nbsp;- aktívna nízka úroveň</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">&nbsp; PORT &amp;= ~(1 &lt;&lt; CE);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#0000CD">// príkaz&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">- nízka úroveň</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">&nbsp; PORT &amp;= ~(1 &lt;&lt; DC);<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// zápis dát do dátového registra, spustenie prenosu</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; SPDR = data;<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// vyčkanie na odoslanie všetkých dát</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#B22222"><strong>while</strong></span> (!(SPSR &amp; (1 &lt;&lt; SPIF)));<br />\r\n&nbsp; <span style="color:#0000CD">// deaktivovanie komunikácie - stav nečinnosti - vysoká úroveň</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; PORT |= (1 &lt;&lt; CE);<br />\r\n}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Na posielanie dát je vytvorená funkcia</span><strong><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px"> DataSend().</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205)"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">// @descr Posielanie dát<br />\r\n// @param uint8_t&nbsp;</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:rgb(0, 100, 0)"><strong>void</strong></span>&nbsp;<strong>DataSend&nbsp;</strong>(<strong><span style="color:rgb(0, 100, 0)">uint8_t</span></strong>&nbsp;data)<br />\r\n{</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">// povolenie komunikácie&nbsp;- aktívna nízka úroveň</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">&nbsp; PORT &amp;= ~(1 &lt;&lt; CE);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205)">// príkaz&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">- vysoká&nbsp;úroveň</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">&nbsp; PORT |= (1 &lt;&lt; DC);</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">// zápis dát do dátového registra, spustenie prenosu</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp; SPDR = data;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">// vyčkanie na odoslanie všetkých dát</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(178, 34, 34); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px"><strong>while</strong></span><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;(!(SPSR &amp; (1 &lt;&lt; SPIF)));</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">// deaktivovanie komunikácie - stav nečinnosti - vysoká úroveň</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp; PORT |= (1 &lt;&lt; CE);</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Vo funkciách&nbsp;<strong>CommandSend()</strong>&nbsp;a <strong>DataSend() </strong>najprv&nbsp;zapíšeme&nbsp;log. 0 na&nbsp;pin&nbsp;CE (Chip Enable, ktorý má&nbsp;aktívnu&nbsp;úroveň&nbsp;log. 0). Vynechaním&nbsp;príkazu, by kontrolér displeja ignoroval posielané hodnoty. Týmto príkazom je displej&nbsp;aktívny príjmať dáta, resp. príkazy. O aký tym&nbsp;posielaných&nbsp;hodnôt&nbsp;sa&nbsp;v skutočnost jedná (dáta alebo príkazy) rozhoduje logická úroveň na pine DC (Data /&nbsp;Command). Ak chceme posielať dáta aktivujeme vysokú&nbsp;logickú úroveň (funkcia <strong>DataSend()</strong>), ak príkazy&nbsp;nízku&nbsp;logickú úroveň (funkcia <strong>CommandSend()</strong>). Po týchto predkrokoch&nbsp;sa dostávamé k samotnému posielaniu dát SPI komunikáciou. Hodnoty (dáta, príkaz), ktoré chceme posielať ukladáme do dátového registra SPDR. Zápisom dát je komunikácia SPI spustená. O ukončení prenosu nás informuje hodnota bitu SPIF v stavovovm registri&nbsp;SPSR. Tým pádom je potrebné iba kontrolovať hodnotou bitu SPIF počas prenosu dovtedy,&nbsp;pokiaľ nie je nastavená&nbsp;na log. 1&nbsp;(tým&nbsp;je&nbsp;prenos ukončený a&nbsp;dáta odoslané). Posledným krokom je ešte </span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">deaktivovanie príjmania dát kontrolérom displeja z</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">ápisom log. 1 na pin CE.</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Po vytvorení potrebných funkcií je ešte dôležité&nbsp;správne nastaviť niektoré parametre. Najprv si vyberieme&nbsp;rozšírenú&nbsp;inštrukčnú&nbsp;sadu vyslaním príkazu s hodnotou&nbsp;0x21.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205)">// rozšírená inštrukčná sada</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">CommandSend(0x21);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Poslaný príkaz&nbsp;rozšíruje&nbsp;nastavenia displeja (tepelný&nbsp;koeficient, bias systém, U<sub>op</sub>). Ako prvý si nastavíme&nbsp;teplotný&nbsp;koeficient, resp. tepelnú&nbsp;kompenzáciu. Tá je dôležitá&nbsp;z toho dôvodu, že viskozita tekutého&nbsp;kryštálu sa&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">v závislosti na teplote&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">mení, čím sa mení aj kontras displeja. Hodnoty, ktoré nám ponúka radič displeja sú vo forme 8 bitového rámca následovné:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="5">\r\n	<caption><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Hodnoty nastavenia teplotného koeficientu displeja</span></span></caption>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB7</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB6</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB5</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB4</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB3</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB2</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">DB0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">HODNOTA</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">POPIS</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x40</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">Tepelný koeficient 0 - horný limit</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x05</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">Tepelný koeficient 1 - typická krivka</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x06</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">Tepelný koeficient 2 - tepelný koeficient radiča</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">1</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x07</span></span></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">Tepelný koeficient 3 - dolný limit</span></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px">V našom prípade je zvolený teplotný koeficient 6 - tepelný koeficient radiča.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">/<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205)">/ nastavenie teplotného koeficientu radiča displeja</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">CommandSend(</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x06);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Ďalším krokom je nastavenie multiplexného pomeru - t. j. počet spoločných elektród (common electrode). V katalógu je uvedený ako optimálny pomer 1/48.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">// bias 1:48 - optimálna hodnota podľa katalógového listu</span>&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">CommandSend(</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x13);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Pre zvolený&nbsp;multiplexný pomer&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">(počet&nbsp;spoločných elektród) definujeme&nbsp;optimálne napätie. V katalógu je uvedený&nbsp;vzťah, podľa ktorého je možné vypočítať optimálne napätie ako 6 V &lt; 3,06 V + (0 x 1 U<sub>cp6</sub> - U<sub>cp0</sub>).0,06&nbsp;V &lt; 8,05 V. V našom prípade bola zvolená zlatá stredná cesta, t. j. 7,02 V čo zodpovedá v hexidecimálnom tvare číslu 0xC2.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">// U<sub>LCD</sub> = 3,06 + (U<sub>cp6</sub> to U<sub>cp0</sub>).0,06, pričom musí platiť&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">6 &lt; U<sub>LCD</sub></span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">&nbsp;&lt; 8,05</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">// U<sub>LCD</sub> = 0x1100 0010 = 7,02 V</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">CommandSend(</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0xC2);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Pred ukončením inicializačnej funkcie aktivujeme&nbsp;normálnu inštrukčnú sadu vyslaním príkazu 0x20 a následne zapneme normálny mód príkazom 0x0C.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">// normálna inštrukčná sada -&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="color:#0000CD">horizontálny adresný mód</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">CommandSend(</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x20);<br />\r\n<span style="color:#0000CD">// normálny mód</span>&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace; font-size:12px">CommandSend(</span><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">0x0C);</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Kompletnú knižnicu je možné stiahnúť pod článkom v sekcii Použité knižnice.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Použité knižnice</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="/Public/file/Atmega8/pcd852/pcd852.c" onclick="window.open(this.href, '''', ''resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=700,left=100,height=700,top=100''); return false;"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-size:12px">pcd852.c</span></span></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><a href="/Public/file/Atmega8/pcd852/pcd852.h" onclick="window.open(this.href, '''', ''resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=700,left=100,height=700,top=100''); return false;">pcd852.h</a></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><a href="/Public/file/Atmega8/pcd852/main.c" onclick="window.open(this.href, '''', ''resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no,width=700,left=100,height=700,top=100''); return false;">main.c</a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Odporúčané odkazy</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/datasheets/LCD/Monochrome/Nokia5110.pdf" target="_blank">https://www.sparkfun.com/datasheets/LCD/Monochrome/Nokia5110.pdf</a></span></span></em></p>\r\n', '2016-10-05 20:20:45', NULL, 'released'),
(28, 1, 'Atmega16', 'atmega16', 'Diel 3 - ošetrenie tlačidla', 'diel-3-switch-debouncing', '<h3 style="text-align:justify">Výpočet hysterézie pre návrh spínača</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">Dôležitou časťou spojenou s elimináciou prekmitov pri spínaní tlačidlového spínača (vyvolávanie externých prerušení, napr. pre prechod v menu) je vytvorenie Schmittovho klopného obvodu s dostatočnou hysteréziou. Jednoducho povedané, je potrebné vytvoriť pásmo necitlivosti pri vznikajúcich prekmitoch spínača. Existuje viacero spôsobov ako sa vysporiadať s týmto javom, napr.:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">softvérovo - vytvorenie časovej podlevy (umelá necitlivosť),</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">hardvérovo - napr. hysterézou pomocou operačného zosilňovača, prípadne priamo Schmittovým klopným obvodom (74HC14)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">V tomto článku bude popísané hardvérové riešenie s jedným operačným zosilňovačom. Podstatou hysterézy je vytvoriť jednú&nbsp;prahovú&nbsp;hodnotu, ktorá&nbsp;musí&nbsp;byť prekročená, aby došlo k preklopeniu na výstupe do saturačnej&nbsp;hodnoty&nbsp;záporného napätia, resp. na potenciál zeme,&nbsp;a druhú hodnotu, pod ktorú napätie na vstupe musí klesnúť, aby došlo k preklopeniu na výstupe do saturačnej hodnoty kladného napájacieho napätia. Rozdiel medzi týmito dvoma prahovými napätiami je pásmo necitlivosti.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">Výpočet prahovej hodnoty na preklopenie výstupného napätia do&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">zápornej</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">&nbsp;saturačnej hodnoty (z úrovne log. 1&nbsp;do log. 0) za predpokladu, že kladné saturačné napätie je rovné napájaciemu napätiu a záporné saturačné napätie&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">je rovné potenciálu&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-size:12px">zeme (0V):</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">U<sub>in</sub>&nbsp;≈ U x&nbsp;[(R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+ R<sub>2</sub>R<sub>3</sub>) / (R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+ R<sub>2</sub>R<sub>3</sub>)]</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Výpočet prahovej hodnoty na preklopenie výstupného napätia do kladnej saturačnej hodnoty (z úrovne log. 0&nbsp;do log. 1) za predpokladu, že kladné saturačné napätie je rovné napájaciemu napätiu a záporné saturačné napätie je rovné potenciálu zeme (0</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">V):</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">U<sub>in</sub>&nbsp;≈&nbsp;U x&nbsp;[R<sub>2</sub>R<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;/ (R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+ R<sub>2</sub>R<sub>3</sub>)]</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Označenie jednotlivých prvkov je uvedené na Obr. 1.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Zlepšenie vlastnosti je možné doplnením dolnopriepriepustného filtra (</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">RC článok</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">) na invertujúci vstup, ktorý integruje vysoké frekvencie a tým je vzrast, resp. pokles napätia miernejší, čo v konečnom dôsledku zlepšuje potlačenie prekmitov spínača.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Jednoduchšou alternátivou je použitie priamo Schmittovho klopného obvodu&nbsp;napríklad obvodom&nbsp;<a href="https://www.nxp.com/documents/data_sheet/74HC_HCT14.pdf" target="_blank">74HC14</a>, ktorý obsahuje šesticu Schmittových klopných obvodov. Výhodou je jednoduchšie zapojenie&nbsp;ale na druhej strane v prípade potreby, nie je možné meniť pásmo necitlivosti (hysterézie).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Na obrázku Obr.1 je uvedené príkladné&nbsp;zapojenie ošetrenia&nbsp;tlačídla pomocou operačného zosilňovača s hodnotami&nbsp;R1 = R3 = 10k<strong>Ω</strong>&nbsp;a R2 = 20 k<strong>Ω</strong>. K preklopeniu dochádza pri napájaní + 5V v hodnote + 4V a + 2V ako je možné vidieť na Obr.2.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/Hysteresis_scheme.png" style="text-align: justify;" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/Hysteresis_scheme.png" style="height:301px; width:400px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11px"><strong>Obr. 1 - Schéma zapojenia operačného zosilľovača s hysteréziou</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/Hysteresis.png" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/Hysteresis.png" style="height:242px; width:500px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Obr. 2&nbsp;- Priebeh napätia na výstupe operačného zosilľovača</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><a href="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/ST_Debouncing.png" style="text-align: justify;" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Public/images/atmel/atmega16/hysteresis/ST_Debouncing.png" style="height:365px; width:300px" /></a><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Obr. 3&nbsp;- Schéma plošného spoja</strong></span></span></p>\r\n', '2016-12-13 06:19:23', NULL, 'draft'),
(30, 1, 'Atmega16', 'atmega16', 'Diel 4 - USART', 'diel-4-usart', '<h3>USART - komunikácia Atmega CP2102</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Cieľom článku je poskytnúť základné informácie potrebné k úspešnej komunikácii medzi 8 bitovým mikrokontrolérom Atmega16 a USB-UART &nbsp; prevodníkom&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">(CP2102)&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">v prostredí operačného systému Ubuntu.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Tvorba knižnice komunikácie USART</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">C library for USART communication of AVR microcontroller Atmega16. Support 7 preddefined baudrates with the smallest baud rate error (-0.1% to 0.2%) for 16 Mhz clock frequency.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Enum types</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Initialisation of USART communitaion is done by function&nbsp;<em>UsartInit()</em>&nbsp;with four mandatory parameters:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">E_baudrate&nbsp;- set baudrate</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">E_framebits&nbsp;- set data frame format</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">E_parity&nbsp;- set parity</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">E_stopbits&nbsp;- set number of stop bits</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(36, 41, 46)">Detailed information about every enum types and values will be&nbsp;described in the next section.</span>&nbsp;Baudrate enum types calculate UBRR value for selected baudrate. There can be added more baudrates as neccessary. The defined baudrates were selected with respect to the smallest calculating baud rate error for 16 Mhz frequency.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">/** @enum UBRR values for different values */\r\ntypedef enum {\r\n  // baudrate  2400 / Error = -0.1% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_2400 = _UBRR(2400),\r\n  // baudrate  4800 / Error =  0.2% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_4800 = _UBRR(4800),\r\n  // baudrate  9600 / Error =  0.2% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_9600 = _UBRR(9600),\r\n  // baudrate  19200 / Error = 0.2% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_19200 = _UBRR(19200),\r\n  // baudrate  38400 / Error = 0.2% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_38400 = _UBRR(38400),\r\n  // baudrate  76800 / Error = 0.2% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_76800 = _UBRR(76800),\r\n  // baudrate 250000 / Error = 0.0% at 16Mhz\r\n  BR_250000 = _UBRR(250000),\r\n} E_baudrate;</span></span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">Framebits enum type defines frame format - number of transmitted and received data bits. Admissible values are 5, 6, 7, 8 and 9 bits</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">/** @enum number of bits - 5, 6, 7, 8, 9 */\r\ntypedef enum {\r\n  // 5 bits\r\n  DATA_5 = 0x00,\r\n  // 6 bits\r\n  DATA_6 = 0x02,\r\n  // 7 bits\r\n  DATA_7 = 0x04,\r\n  // 8 bits\r\n  DATA_8 = 0x06,\r\n  // 9 bits\r\n  DATA_9 = 0x1\r\n} E_framebits;</span></span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Parity enum type defines parity of data frame. Allowable values are disable parity, even parity - add one if the number of ones in data data frame is odd, and odd parity - add one if number of ones in data frame is even.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">/** @enum parity - none, even, odd */\r\ntypedef enum {\r\n  // none\r\n  PARITY_NONE = 0x00,\r\n  // even\r\n  PARITY_EVEN = 0x20,\r\n  // odd\r\n  PARITY_ODD  = 0x30\r\n} E_parity;</span></span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif">The last mandatory parameter in init function for USART communication is number of stop bits. There are two allowable values - 1 stop bit, 2 stop bits.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">/** @enum stop bits - 1, 2 */\r\ntypedef enum {\r\n  // 1 stop bit\r\n  STOPBITS_1 = 0x00,\r\n  // 2 stop bits\r\n  STOPBITS_2 = 0x20\r\n} E_stopbits;</span></span>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<h4>Odkazy</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://elinux.org/Communicate_with_hardware_using_USB_cable_for_Ubuntu" target="_blank"><em><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,monospace">http://elinux.org/Communicate_with_hardware_using_USB_cable_for_Ubuntu</span></span></em></a></p>\r\n', '2017-07-12 10:39:16', NULL, 'draft');

